article_title: Rand Paul signs up for Obamacare exchange: 'Made me an unhappy person'
article_text: U.S. Sen. Rand Paul, an outspoken opponent of President Barack Obama's health care law, described his frustration upon signing up for the Washington, D.C., exchange, which the senator did Wednesday.
